_sText:
This is my first map on the site and my first deathrun map. If you find any bugs/glitches, please pm me. 

Includes:
15 traps
A ct spawnkiller with a 60 second delay.
When the counterterrorist(s) get to the end they can choose between a knife fight with the terrorist(s) or go to the terrorist area and shoot them.

Enjoy
